pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 01:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-slip-china-demand-concerns-waning-middle-east-worries-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储、日本央行面前的等待游戏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 21:48:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>体操-日本队在激动人心的决赛中击败中国队夺得男子团体金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japan-win-mens-team-gold-2024-07-29/</link><description>桥本大树周一在巴黎奥运会体操男子团体决赛中战胜了中国队，从鞍马上摔倒，最终夺得金牌，他将心痛变成了难以想象的喜悦。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:14:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-japan-win-mens-team-gold-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>情报官员称，外国势力将寻求影响重塑的美国总统竞选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/foreign-influence-actors-adapt-us-presidential-race-changes-says-intelligence-2024-07-29/</link><description>一名美国情报官员周一表示，针对 11 月大选进行影响力行动的美国敌人预计将适应总统竞选的发展，这显然是指乔·拜登放弃连任竞选。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/foreign-influence-actors-adapt-us-presidential-race-changes-says-intelligence-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：SpaceX 正在洽谈在澳大利亚海岸着陆并回收星舰火箭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-talks-land-recover-starship-rocket-off-australias-coast-2024-07-29/</link><description>据三位知情人士透露，SpaceX 正在与美国和澳大利亚官员进行谈判，以在澳大利亚海岸着陆并回收其一艘 Starship 火箭，这可能是埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的公司在该地区扩大业务的第一步，因为两国加强了安全关系。与计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-talks-land-recover-starship-rocket-off-australias-coast-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国间谍还是反革命？外国特工审判在布鲁克林开始</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/trial-begins-us-citizen-accused-acting-chinese-agent-2024-07-29/</link><description>美国检方指控一名中国学者在周一对这位 76 岁的外国特工指控的审判开始时向北京出卖了美国的异见人士，而辩护律师则表示，他们的当事人正试图为共产主义中国带来民主。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/trial-begins-us-citizen-accused-acting-chinese-agent-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>白宫称乌克兰援助计划价值高达2亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-aid-package-valued-up-200-million-white-house-says-2024-07-29/</link><description>白宫国家安全发言人约翰·柯比表示，美国周一宣布了一项针对乌克兰的新安全援助计划，价值高达 2 亿美元，其中包括防空系统和反坦克武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-aid-package-valued-up-200-million-white-house-says-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平和意大利总理梅洛尼在北京会面讨论冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-calls-balanced-eu-china-trade-xi-meeting-2024-07-29/</link><description>梅洛尼办公室称，中国国家主席习近平和意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周一在北京举行会议，讨论了乌克兰战争和中东危机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-calls-balanced-eu-china-trade-xi-meeting-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球-朝鲜晋级混双决赛挑战中国 勒布伦兄弟晋级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-fan-chen-cruise-past-first-round-paris-2024-07-29/</link><description>朝鲜神秘的混双队击败香港队，晋级决赛，与强大的中国队一决高下，八年来首次获得奥运会奖牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-fan-chen-cruise-past-first-round-paris-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示全球经济增长弹性与降息预期不符</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economys-growing-resilience-odds-with-rate-cut-expectations-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透社调查的数百名经济学家对今年和明年全球增长前景的乐观情绪正在增强，尽管他们坚持降息预测，但风险仍然倾向于通胀上升。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economys-growing-resilience-odds-with-rate-cut-expectations-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳全球销售额三年多来首次下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-posts-surprise-drop-quarterly-global-sales-spending-slows-2024-07-29/</link><description>麦当劳周一报告称，其全球销售额意外下降，这是 13 个季度以来的首次下降，原因是寻求优惠的消费者避开了包括巨无霸在内的价格较高的菜单项。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-posts-surprise-drop-quarterly-global-sales-spending-slows-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>羽毛球-中国队巴黎连胜被马来西亚人和丹麦人终结</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-malaysia-ends-chinas-paris-winning-streak-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，中国队在巴黎奥运会上遭遇羽毛球首场失利，混双热门选手冯彦哲和黄东萍不敌马来西亚组合，而中国男双队则被丹麦队击败。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-malaysia-ends-chinas-paris-winning-streak-2024-07-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>